{"tid":1631651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"利用whatsapp轉傳 讓藍絲加入戰局","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:00:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:56:13.000Z","uid":295039,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5a51ded9ab5a41667f76b7b31e5617ebcf5e1d2c","tid":1631651,"uid":295039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:00:26.000Z","msg":"大家都知道 <br />\n有年紀的中老年藍絲是最不動腦的<br />\n所以他們會信政府/共黨的宣傳<br />\n會信WhatsApp 轉傳 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n既然現在中共愛發假新聞/假訊息 <br />\n我們就要用其人之道還制其人之身 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n譬如想讓藍絲去銀行擠兌<br />\n<br />\n就發一條有真有假的訊讓藍絲轉傳：<br />\n金融大鱷Kyle bass 表示，香港緊急法實行，銀行擠兌，前景堪慮。 香港政府爲維金融制序，料將限制每日提領限額，附圖 。 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XbCGAZr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXbCGAZr.png&h=92215e8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這裡面圖是真的 Kyle bass 說的是真的 <br />\n政府限提領的 是假的 但能達成讓藍絲去提款<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有真假訊息混合 藍絲智力本就不夠<br />\n這下更無法確認訊息真偽 更會去提領<br />\n提領了還會再轉傳 效果更大 <br />\n<br />\n大家都做<br />\n不同的人 會做出不同的假訊息 <br />\n找來的真訊息不會一樣 但目的都是讓藍絲提領<br />\n那藍絲看到這麼多訊息 都是要趕快去提領 <br />\n一定無法分辯真偽 必去提領 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這下大家都去提領 擠兌就完成了 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不管是什麼目的 都可以如法炮製<br />\n這樣藍絲也爲我所用 不再是唱反調的一群了<br />\n<br />\n否則像之前那樣 講到死藍絲都不會做"},{"pid":"93f19d6b4f1ba5dfb1fca2099bac7580f73b4925","tid":1631651,"uid":30113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:01:40.000Z","msg":"行動post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82e720874078d242db4bfcccfb34fd0c55a8b130","tid":1631651,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:02:11.000Z","msg":"以彼之道還施彼身<br />\n【地方的手足需要進化】麻煩大家入黎溫下書，睇下烏克蘭係E個時候做左D咩<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631278\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631278</a>"},{"pid":"ad9e6858d1d1b0723d24f0769fff87cb4ddc1d22","tid":1631651,"uid":19278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:03:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d290134741d231b0eccdb7a1cee9ae8797f71109","tid":1631651,"uid":295039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:11:01.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"cd811995c6b64d4a9451caee222d342663a5bd64","tid":1631651,"uid":295039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:22:02.000Z","msg":"自推上熱門"},{"pid":"cdb5e802e43e1be4c25a3ec2e518753746c9d369","tid":1631651,"uid":295039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:56:13.000Z","msg":"自推"}]}